Loka Ekapolokiton lueruos. Esabuli loka Daudi.


1  Wu Edeke, kiiranari eporotoka, kotoma akadanakinika:

Kidarenenei aijaraka kenyek akurianar yenikasurup.


2  

Kisinopai eoŋ kama ejai ainerun nakaiyeiyea naka ikeswamak nukaronok;

Kama ejai ecelet loka ikeswamak numam edolito.


3  

Luepenata aŋajepekec kwape ekileŋ,

Luetebeikis imaliakec, kes akiro nuedwarak:


4  Tetere egumete iŋol loedoliorit toma aiboisio nukaiyeiyea:

Enesarete aigum ŋes, komam ekuriaka.


5  Isidikete itauonokec kotoma ainerun aronis:

Inerununete ailok iica kaiyeiyea;

Kobalas ebe, “Iŋai eanyuni kes?”


6  Emoete numam edolito;

Kobalas ebe, “Kidau akukunyikin aimo noi.”

Idul aomisioit nakotoma naka ŋinituŋanan ka etau da.


7  Konye egumi kes Edeke;

Enesario aimusuŋ kemal.


8  

Iguanakinos kwaŋin, idupori kes aŋajepekec:

Kere lueanyunete kes imuŋumuŋete akwesikec.


9  Ekuriakaros ituŋa kere;

Elimorete da aswam naka Edeke,

Eomoomoete akeswamisio kacoa.


10  

Iyalamikinos ikadolitok kotoma EJAKAIT,

Emunokinos da ŋes;

Iturete luitenara kotauon.

